OL,3,CAt least 287 Nigerian students
OL,4,Cabducted from school by gunmen,
OL,5,Cauthorities say
OL,7,FGunman attacked and abducted at least
OL,8,F287 students at a school in north-west
OL,9,FNigeria, the headteacher told
OL,10,Fauthorities.
OL,12,FThe incident marks the second mass
OL,13,Fabduction in the in less than a week.
OL,15,FAssailants surrounded the government-
OL,16,Fowned school in Kaduna State's Kuriga
OL,17,Ftown just before pupils were about to
OL,18,Fstart the school day, according to
OL,19,Flocals.
