OL,3,CAt least 287 Nigerian students
OL,4,Cabducted from school by gunmen,
OL,5,Cauthorities say
OL,7,FAuthorities had initially said more
OL,8,Fthan 100 students were taken hostage
OL,9,Fin the attack. However, the
OL,10,Fheadteacher confirmed the number was
OL,11,Fcloser to 300 after a headcount.
OL,13,FAbductions of students from schools in
OL,14,Fnorthern Nigeria are common and have
OL,15,Fbecome a growing source of concern
OL,16,Fafter 200 girls were kidnapped by
OL,17,FIslamic extremists from a school in
OL,18,F2014.
