OL,3,CAt least 287 Nigerian students
OL,4,Cabducted from school by gunmen,
OL,5,Cauthorities say
OL,7,FIn recent years, the abductions have
OL,8,Fbeen concentrated in north-western and
OL,9,Fcentral regions, where dozens of armed
OL,10,Fgroups often target villagers and
OL,11,Ftravellers for huge ransoms.
OL,13,FSani Abdullahi, the headteacher,
OL,14,Fhowever, told Kaduna Governor Uba Sani
OL,15,Fwhen he visited the town the total
OL,16,Fnumber of those missing after a
OL,17,Fheadcount was 287.
