OL,3,CAt least 287 Nigerian students
OL,4,Cabducted from school by gunmen,
OL,5,Cauthorities say
OL,7,F"We will ensure that every child will
OL,8,Fcome back. We are working with the
OL,9,Fsecurity agencies," the governor told
OL,10,Fvillagers in the area located 55 miles
OL,11,Ffrom the capital.
OL,13,FNo group claimed responsibility for
OL,14,FThursday's attack though blame fell on
OL,15,Farmed groups that mostly constitute
OL,16,Fherders who have been accused of
OL,17,Fcarrying out violent attacks and
OL,18,Fkidnappings for ransom following
OL,19,Fdecades-long pastoral conflict with
OL,20,Fhost communities.
