OL,5,Cauthorities say
OL,7,FSecurity forces arrived with the
OL,8,Fgovernor several hours later as a
OL,9,Fsearch operation widened, while
OL,10,Fcommunity members and parents gathered
OL,11,Fto wait for news.
OL,13,FThe attack occurred days after more
OL,14,Fthan 200 people, mostly women and
OL,15,Fchildren, were abducted by extremists
OL,16,Fin north-eastern Nigeria.
