OL,7,FWomen, children and students are often
OL,8,Ftargeted in the mass abductions in the
OL,9,Fconflict-hit northern region and many
OL,10,Fvictims are released only after paying
OL,11,Fhuge ransoms.
OL,13,FObservers say both attacks are a
OL,14,Freminder of Nigeria's worsening
OL,15,Fsecurity crisis which resulted in the
OL,16,Fdeaths of several hundred people in
OL,17,F2023.
